org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.its.datastructs.basic

Class Duration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.its.datastructs.basic.Duration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StructSerializer

    public class Duration
extends Object
implements StructSerializer
    This uint16 encodes the duration of a time span (e.g. a certificate's validity). The first three bits shall encode the units as given in table 3. The remaining 13 bits shall be treated as an integer encoded in network byte order.
    Author:
    Philip Vendil
